ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Transfer to PMG Technologies Inc. of the use of Certain Movable Public Properties
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Transport to TRANSFER to PMG TECHNOLOGIES INC. the use of certain movable public properties listed in or contemplated by contract T8127-050001/001/MTA made by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services, pertaining to the operation and maintenance of the Motor Vehicle Test Centre at Blainville, Quebec, for the period commencing on October 27, 2022 and ending on October 26, 2024.
